[Student "S"]
{WEST opens 2\C and is pleased when EAST makes a positive response of 2\S. 
His first step is to set the trump suit by bidding 3\S. There is NO chance that EAST will pass.

EAST now bids 4\C a Control-showing bid. 
WEST continues Control-showing with 4\D.

That's enough for EAST to hear. She invokes Blackwood and learning they have all the Aces 
bids 7\S.}

